        <abstract>
            <p>Another plea to take Scott on at Kew. Emma begs CD not to employ him at Down.</p> 
<p>Has just received a long article on the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> from D. J. Brown, an Edinburgh baker [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4464</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
